headline: Nordson’s (NASDAQ:NDSN) Q2 Sales Top Estimates
summary: Manufacturing company Nordson (NASDAQ:NDSN) reported Q2 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 12.1% year on year to $741.5 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.73 per share was 3.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Nordson: Fiscal Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: WESTLAKE, Ohio (AP) — Nordson Corp. NDSN) on Wednesday reported fiscal third-quarter profit of $125.8 million. The Westlake, Ohio-based company said it had profit of $2.22 per share.
